==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Gasify
<hw>Gas"i*fy</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>v. i.</pos> <def>To become gas; to
pass from a liquid to a gaseous state.</def> <rj><au>Scientific
American.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

